pageContext.content:
Hardcore Skaterockers, Frontside Five, defeat death once again! Their latest full length release capusures the band’s pure essence of skate punk. it is laced with driving anthems, tempo changes, thrash riffs, and lyrics that will stick into your head well into the afterlife.

“Their music is everything you’d want in a skate rock band. It’s fast, driving, fun punk rock, with some heavy breakdowns.” -Thrasher Magazine
